# --- Documentation Images (Crucial) ---
# Ensure your images are NOT ignored. 
# If you want to ignore all images EXCEPT those in your notes/img_section:
# *.png
# *.jpg
# !notes/img_section/*.png
# !notes/img_section/*.jpg

